@startuml
actor Coach
title Coach Request Facility
participant "Web App" as WA
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "App Server" as AS
database "DB" as DB

Coach -> WA: Selects facility & submits booking request
WA -> API: Send booking request
API -> AS: Forward request for processing
AS -> DB: Read facility availability
DB --> AS: Availability data
AS -> DB: Write new booking
DB --> AS: Confirmation
AS --> API: Booking result
API --> WA: Return success/failure
WA --> Coach: Show booking confirmation
@enduml
